    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, preheat the grill to medium-high</p><p>Peel and finely slice your<strong> brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Deseed your <strong>pepper[s]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span></strong>(scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into thin strips</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
