    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Pour the <strong>egg mixture </strong>into the pan, pressing the vegetables down, and cook for 3-4 min or until the egg starts to brown on the bottom</p><p>Once brown, put the pan under the grill for 4-6 min or until the egg has set – this is your <strong>veg-packed Spanish-style omelette</strong></p><p>Tip: Make sure you leave the pan handle outside of the oven and the door open whilst grilling!</p>",
