    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the omelette is cooking, wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Combine the <strong>remaining chopped garlic </strong>and <strong>mayo </strong>together with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>– this is your <strong>garlic aioli</strong></p>",
