      "instruction": "<p>Slice the <strong>veg-packed Spanish-style omelette</strong> into quarters and serve with the <strong>salad </strong>and <strong>garlic aioli </strong>to the side</p><p>Drizzle the salad with your <strong>cider vinegar </strong>and 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
